{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01VPVNte8cUzW7Gd4RSiswi2","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01BH69BXYKzDzVn7KbgF8d13","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Whipped Goat Cheese Dip.generated.22.txt","content":"WHIPPED GOAT CHEESE DIP\n\nThis delightful appetizer hails from the Mediterranean, where goat cheese has been\na staple for centuries. The creamy, tangy richness of fresh chèvre pairs beautifully\nwith bright herbs and roasted garlic, creating a dip that's elegant yet approachable.\nI first encountered this recipe at a small bistro in Provence, and it has since become\na favorite party appetizer in my home. The key to success is starting with the highest\nquality goat cheese you can find—it truly makes all the difference.\n\nIngredients:\n8 oz fresh goat cheese, at room temperature\n4 oz cream cheese, softened\n3 cloves roasted garlic, minced\n2 tablespoons fresh dill, chopped\n1 tablespoon fresh thyme leaves\n2 tablespoons fresh chives, chopped\n2 tablespoons extra virgin olive oil\n1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice\nSalt and white pepper to taste\nZest of 1 lemon\nCrusty bread or crackers for serving\n\nMethod:\nCombine goat cheese and cream cheese in a food processor. Blend until smooth\nand creamy, about 2-3 minutes. Add roasted garlic, dill, thyme, and chives.\nPulse gently to combine without over-mixing.\n\nTransfer to a serving bowl and drizzle with olive oil. Sprinkle with lemon\nzest and season with salt and white pepper. Serve with crusty bread and\nfresh vegetables.\n\nMakes about 1 1/2 cups.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":619,"cache_read_input_tokens":107703,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":619},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be930ac5-73c9-4a08-804e-ef9f978d1268","uuid":"6cda3d7c-6c86-4e74-ae82-46aebde2c961"}
