{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_014RV1pb5dMmtmJg5uJs2Nbv","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01FoYgo7UveykAkowVCpfUee","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Cardamom Chai Tea.generated.22.txt","content":"CARDAMOM CHAI TEA\n\nThere's nothing quite like the warming embrace of a proper chai on a cold winter's day.\nThis spiced tea, inspired by the tea stalls of India and perfected over many afternoons\nspent in comfortable kitchens, brings together the warmth of spices with the comfort of\nmilk. The cardamom pods are the star here—bruised just slightly to release their oils,\nthey infuse the entire pot with an intoxicating aroma. My grandmother used to make this\nevery Sunday morning, and I remember the kitchen filling with this spicy, sweet steam\nbefore we'd even sit down to breakfast. It's a recipe meant for sharing, for slowing\ndown, and for enjoying life's simple pleasures.\n\nIngredients:\n4 cups water\n4 green cardamom pods, slightly crushed\n4 black peppercorns\n2 cinnamon sticks, about 3 inches each\n4 whole cloves\n1 inch piece fresh ginger, sliced\n4 black tea bags or 4 teaspoons loose black tea\n2 tablespoons honey or sugar\n3/4 cup whole milk\nPinch of sea salt\n\nMethod:\nBring water to a boil in a pot. Add cardamom pods, peppercorns, cinnamon,\ncloves, and ginger. Simmer for 5 minutes to infuse the spices.\n\nAdd black tea and simmer for another 3-4 minutes. Don't over-steep or the tea\nwill become bitter. Stir in honey and salt to taste.\n\nWarm the milk separately and gently pour into each cup along with the spiced tea.\nStrain the spices through a fine mesh if desired, though some prefer them left in.\n\nServes 4. Best enjoyed hot with biscuits or pastries.\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":829,"cache_read_input_tokens":108904,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":829},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"be930ac5-73c9-4a08-804e-ef9f978d1268","uuid":"46a79c61-b869-4a8a-b696-60a35f9ec4f8"}
